OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776228833
OL,3,CWatchdog bans first ads under new
OL,4,C'less healthy' food rules
OL,6,FAds for supermarkets Lidl and Iceland
OL,7,Fhave become the first to be banned
OL,8,Funder new rules governing "less
OL,9,Fhealthy" food and drink.
OL,11,FThe rules, which came into effect at
OL,12,Fthe beginning of the year, are part of
OL,13,FGovernment efforts to tackle childhood
OL,14,Fobesity by preventing ads for food and
OL,15,Fdrink that is high in fat, salt and
OL,16,Fsugar (HFSS) appearing on television
OL,17,Fbetween 5.30am and 9pm, and online at
OL,18,Fany time.
OL,26,@pD@[OUqD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
