OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776228833
OL,3,CWatchdog bans first ads under new
OL,4,C'less healthy' food rules
OL,6,FThe new ban applies to products that
OL,7,Ffall within 13 categories considered
OL,8,Fto play the most significant role in
OL,9,Fchildhood obesity, including soft
OL,10,Fdrinks, chocolates and sweets, pizzas
OL,11,Fand ice creams, but also breakfast
OL,12,Fcereals and porridges, sweetened bread
OL,13,Fproducts, and main meals and
OL,14,Fsandwiches.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776228833
OL,3,CWatchdog bans first ads under new
OL,4,C'less healthy' food rules
OL,6,FProducts that fall into these
OL,7,Fcategories are than also assessed as
OL,8,Fto whether they are "less healthy"
OL,9,Fbased on a scoring tool that considers
OL,10,Ftheir nutrient levels and whether
OL,11,Fproducts are high in saturated fat,
OL,12,Fsalt or sugar.
OL,14,FOnly products that meet both of the
OL,15,Ftwo criteria are included in the
OL,16,Frestrictions.
OL,26,@pD@UOUpD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
