OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776228833
OL,3,CWatchdog bans first ads under new
OL,4,C'less healthy' food rules
OL,6,FThe Advertising Standards Authority
OL,7,F(ASA) said an Instagram post for Lidl
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland by influencer Emma
OL,9,FKearney featured the grocer's cheese
OL,10,Fpretzel, which was not categorised as
OL,11,FHFSS and therefore did not fall within
OL,12,Fthe restrictions, and its Pain Suisse
OL,13,Fproduct, which was classified as both
OL,14,FHFSS and a sweetened bread product and
OL,15,Fwas therefore banned under the new
OL,16,Frules.
OL,18,FLidl said the ad had been removed and
OL,19,Fthey had liaised with their marketing
OL,20,Fagency to ensure that all future ads
OL,21,Fcomplied with the new rules.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776228833
OL,3,CWatchdog bans first ads under new
OL,4,C'less healthy' food rules
OL,6,FIn a separate case, Iceland confirmed
OL,7,Fthat two ads included a tub of
OL,8,FSwizzles Sweet Treats, a packet of
OL,9,FChupa Chups Laces, a bag of Chooee
OL,10,FDisco Stix and a bag of Haribo Elf
OL,11,FSurprises, which were all classified
OL,12,Fas HFSS.
OL,14,FThey also provided nutrient profile
OL,15,Finformation from their supplier which
OL,16,Fconfirmed that Pringles Sour Cream &
OL,17,FOnion crisps, also included in the
OL,18,Fads, were not an HFSS product.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776228833
OL,3,CWatchdog bans first ads under new
OL,4,C'less healthy' food rules
OL,6,FIceland's Luxury Aberdeen Angus Beef
OL,7,FRoasting Joint, Vegetable Spring
OL,8,FRolls, Sticky Chicken Skewers and
OL,9,FLurpak Spreadable Butter, which were
OL,10,Falso included in the ads, did not fall
OL,11,Fwithin the new restrictions.
OL,13,FThe ASA did not uphold a complaint
OL,14,Fagainst an Instagram post by
OL,15,Finfluencer John Fisher ` known to many
OL,16,Fas Big John ` which featured him
OL,17,Fpromoting menu items at a new German
OL,18,FDoner Kebab outlet because the
OL,19,Fspecific items shown in the ad were
OL,20,Fnot classified as less healthy foods.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776228833
OL,3,CWatchdog bans first ads under new
OL,4,C'less healthy' food rules
OL,6,FThe watchdog also cleared a TV ad for
OL,7,FOn The Beach promoting free airport
OL,8,Flounge access which featured a boy
OL,9,Fapproaching a buffet and taking a
OL,10,Fchocolate ring doughnut.
OL,12,FThe ASA said viewers would see the ad
OL,13,Fas showing an example of what was
OL,14,Favailable in the lounge rather than
OL,15,Ffor the doughnut itself, meaning it
OL,16,Fdid not break the rules.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776228833
OL,3,CWatchdog bans first ads under new
OL,4,C'less healthy' food rules
OL,6,FASA chief executive Guy Parker said:
OL,7,F"As the ad regulator, our role is to
OL,8,Fremain impartial and independent,
OL,9,Fmaking sure our new LHF rules, which
OL,10,Freflect the law, are applied fairly
OL,11,Fand consistently.
OL,13,F"These initial rulings are an
OL,14,Fimportant step in building a clearer
OL,15,Fpicture of how the rules are applied
OL,16,Fin reality.
OL,18,F"We'll be continuing to play our role
OL,19,Fin administering and enforcing them,
OL,20,Fincluding by using tech-assisted
OL,21,Fproactive monitoring."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUzD@AOU}D@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
