OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776228833
OL,3,CWatchdog bans first ads under new
OL,4,C'less healthy' food rules
OL,6,FAn Iceland spokesman said: "The
OL,7,Fproducts highlighted were part of a
OL,8,Fbigger range in the specific display
OL,9,Fad and were featured due to a
OL,10,Ftechnical fault with a data feed from
OL,11,Fa third-party supplier.
OL,13,F"As the ASA has pointed out, these
OL,14,Finitial rulings are helping to build a
OL,15,Fclearer picture of how the new rules
OL,16,Fare applied, following the initial
OL,17,Fconfusion and debate around the
OL,18,Fregulations."
OL,26,@nD@\OUuD@AOUzD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/9
